name: Interactive Book Collection # Cinderella
description:
This book is part of the Interactive Book Collection, published by justlows.

Since this NFT is interactive, it is possible to read the entire book! You can flip the pages by clicking and dragging or by using your arrow keys of the keyboard.


Cinderella is a fairy tale collected by the Brothers Grimm, about a young woman living in forsaken circumstances that are suddenly changed to remarkable fortune, with her ascension to the throne via marriage.
